feedback.comment: Ishir, these are great questions to ask yourself to get started on your AP portfolio journey. However, the "Inquiry" for the sustained investigation should be more specific and geared towards what you can demonstrate to your audience. So you can take your ideas formed here and push them a bit farther. For example, your questions of "What emotions do I want to embody through my artwork?" can be turned into an inquiry such as " "How can I demonstrate feelings of nostalgia through (insert art medium or process here)". The drawing looks great so far!
